This paper is primarily focused on optimization algorithms for machine learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses communication efficiency in distributed optimization, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Additionally, the paper includes numerical analyses on real datasets, which could fall under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
